data.description:
Welcome to your new home! No Metro District! Views of the Rocky Mountains and Boyd Lake from every room in the house! The location of this wonderful 4 Bed, 4 Bath, plus Office Space Cottage home is unbeatable! You won't find a house with these views for this price, out there! Your new home features a beautiful French Door entryway, updated kitchen with Luxury Quartz Countertops, Honeycomb Backsplash, Gas Range, Soft Close Cabinet Doors, and an oversized single-tub stainless steel sink. Your master suite hosts a see-through fireplace from your five-piece master bath ensuite, equipped with an oversized soaker tub and two shower heads. The basement hosts a wet bar for entertaining, 4th bedroom for guests, extra storage space, and a large walk-in rain-head shower with two shower heads! Need space to park extra vehicles!? You'll love the 3-car oversized and extended garage with loft space for even more storage! Easily park trucks, campers, or toys!

Landscaping is complete with a new vinyl privacy fence, 2 Peach Trees, 2 Pear Trees, above-ground garden boxes, several vines, flowers, and mature trees. No need to worry about watering your plants and tress with a new Beehive smart sprinkler system in front and back.  

*Home is equipped with a tankless hot water heater, whole-house humidifier, whole-house air purification filtration system.

Elementary school is a 2 minute walk away! Parks, Trails, Resivors and Community Garden Center within walking distance. Close to shopping centers and outlet malls. Target, Scheels, and In and Out, to name a few. Easy access to I-25 if you commute and MCR UCHealth Hospital just down the road. Close to all the amenities you need with an outstanding Lake and Mountain view!
*Home comes with a Blue Ribbon Home Warranty Package to include all major appliances including the A/C*
